Package: hollr
Type: Package
Title: "A lightweight, versatile tool for text completion via local and cloud-based LLMs in R."
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Jason Timm [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Jason Timm <JaTimm@salud.unm.edu>
